ent-RMCBarricadeRazorwire = razorwire
    .desc = A set of razorwire, able to slow down anything that tries to move through it. Cut with wirecutters to disable, then unwrench to recover.

ent-RMCBarricadeRazorwireCut = cut razorwire
    .desc = A set of razorwire that has been cut. No longer functional. Use a wrench to tear it up and recover the remaining wire.
